com.kulana.core.foundation.webdriver.locator

Class ExtendedElementLocator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kulana.core.foundation.webdriver.locator.ExtendedElementLocator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openqa.selenium.support.pagefactory.ElementLocator

    public class ExtendedElementLocator
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.openqa.selenium.support.pagefactory.ElementLocator
    The default element locator, which will lazily locate an element or an element list on a page. This class is designed for use with the PageFactory and understands the annotations FindBy and CacheLookup.
